    "For papers which only compare to variations of their proposed model, we attempt to highlight the performance effects of any CI-related components.",
    "For papers which experiment on multiple datasets with varying levels of imbalance, we provide ρ for the most imbalanced dataset, if this information is available.",
    "Double lines between table rows indicate the subsection divisions between the surveyed papers.We note that there are many works which apply \"trivial\" CI methods (see \"Common non-LSL approaches to CI\" section) independent of the rest of the model, and thus are not included in the body of this survey nor in Table 1.",
